{"tid":1807682,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動Post]自稱黃嘅同我入黎，無論你係淺黃定係金","createTime":"2020-01-02T02:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T15:44:05.000Z","uid":196018,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1079b9f43d3d70d2a5fc77e43d6baca4d18350c3","tid":1807682,"uid":196018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"首先第一，革命都半年啦，講左幾耐唔好撚再捉鬼，原因我唔想再講，我相信大家都知，由下次岀黎開始，邊撚個再捉鬼就當佢係鬼，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">私左再講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第二，都係個句，革命都半年啦，邊撚個再做散水撚都係個句，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">私左再講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地諗下1月1號，你地做過啲乜，全日都係到捉鬼加做散水撚，岀撚到黎講句1月5號上水見，咁你地岀黎做乜鳩，我地打緊仗呀，唔係岀黎做show嫁，乜撚野只係見到狗車就係咁鳩走，啲狗連地都未落，就話走走走，唔夠打<br />\n<br />\n我唔該你地，和理非升級嘅，唔識唔緊要，唔好係到鳩講野，試下聽下一啲打左耐啲嘅人講野，真係唔識嘅，真係唔緊要，學就可以，但唔該你地唔好鳩黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後講多次，再捉鬼再做散水撚，私撚左再傾</span></span>"},{"pid":"5453624f247de0d56db0fa58750b3f7e266e988a","tid":1807682,"uid":196018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:02:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5718e70fbd9eb65fd7977569928f4536241d6e04","tid":1807682,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"你呢段野既target audience係non lihkg user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28044ddf9deeaed0229241ce942a39f8b473794","tid":1807682,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5718e70fbd9eb65fd7977569928f4536241d6e04","tid":1807682,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"你呢段野既target audience係non lihkg user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"哦 你分化<br />\n哦 你熱狗<br />\nBtw<br />\n捉到狗又點呀<br />\n成班和理非都唔敢做嘢<br />\n捉咗手足就仆街<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: ora